I"@<h2 id="create-the-symbolic-link">Create The Symbolic Link</h2>

<p>example:</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">$ sudo ln -s /home/matt/Documents/Git /opt/lampp/htdocs</code></p>

<p>To create a symlink without a terminal, just hold Shift+Ctrl and drag the file or folder you want to link to</p>
